Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)

Phase 1: Define the problem to be solved
Phase 2: Design a solution to the problem
Phase 3: Write a program that implements the solution
Phase 4: Compile the program
Phase 5: Link object files
Phase 6: Test and debug program

